Working side by side they built a successful and thriving business that to this day still prides itself on the quality of the products it produces.Â 

Chris and Marina have been retired a long time now and the business is in the hands of the next generation of their family. It remains the epitome of a small Australian family based business. That owes its success to the quality ethos passed on by Chris and Marina since the very beginning. Today. The Antoniou family continues to specialise in filo pastry at our state of the art facility.
